snippet.title: Alohomora - The True Emperor (Lyrical) | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe üëâ https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Alohomora - The True Emperor'' from the movie ''The Devil'' starring Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai and others. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. 

Song Credits:
Name: Alohomora - The True Emperor
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By: B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer: Aniruddha Sastry
Lyrics: Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer: Santhu Master
Keyboard: B Ajaneesh Loknath, Raja Ravi Varma
Rhythm: B Ajaneesh Loknath, Kalyan Chakravarthy
Electric Guitars: Sam Sundar, Viyaan Veer
Chorus: ASR Choir Team Supreeth Phalguna, Abhishek MR, Hrushikesh BR, ASR
Choir Conducted & Recorded By: Aniruddha Sastry
Song Mixed & Masterd By: Pukhraj Sonkar
Assistant Engineer: Dipesh Dhruw Inhouse Studio Mumbai
Music Production: C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, ABBS Studios Bangalore

Production Team:
Produced By : J Jayamma & Saregama
Banner : Shri Jai Matha Combines
Directed By : Prakash Veer
Executive Producer : Thashwini Veer
Dialogue : Kanthraj S S
Costumes : Chethan & Thashwini Veer
Direction Department : Mohan Malagi, M S Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth

Technical Team:
Director Of Photography : Sudhakarr S Raj
Music Director : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Editor : Harish Komme
Song Editor : Sohan Galgali
Online Editor : Naveen Shetty
Art Director : Mohan B Kere
Action Director : Ram Lakshman
Colourist : Vivek Anand
Post Production : Annapurna Studios
CG & VFX : Trayom Studios
Managers : Suresh K Mysore, Jagadish Rao R
Still Photography : Kadur Raghu & Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video : Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Subtitle : Ashwin Sriram
Publicity Design : Kaani Studio
Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PR & Marketing : Purvi Kulkarni
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh
Digital PR : Pavan Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Pallavi:
Alohomora The True Emperor
Doubtey Beda Saitaanu Devare..
Astalavista Helade Iro
Bandhanadale Takaraaru Tondare

Kaliyugadee Krishna Yaarole
Asali Kali Yaaru Helale ?
Huttuvudu Saavinindale
Beta Belaku Baap Hai Kattale

If There Is A Will
You‚Äôll Find Evil
Brace Yourself And See
Who‚Äôs The Real Devil ‚Ä¶.
Cho - Ratatatata
Cho - All Rise For The Devil ‚Ä¶.

Charana:
Surya Chandra Milanaane Grahana
Sihi Maatina Hinde Kahi Marma Mouna

Srishti Huttu Drishteene Saavu
Baduku Bella Annode Bevu

Mukhaavadada Badukannu Bodhisuvane Katuka
Usiraatake Koneyelli Husi Iruvaa Tanaka

Janana Marana Naduve Vyasana Payana
Parama Satya Onde Jagada Nidhana

Kaliyugadee Krishna Yaarole
Asali Kali Yaaru Helale ?
Huttuvudu Saavinindale
Beta Belaku Baap Hai Kattale

If There Is A Will
You‚Äôll Find Evil
Brace Yourself And See
Who‚Äôs The Real Devil ‚Ä¶.

Cho - Ratatatata


Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

snippet.title: Varanasi Movie Story Explained in Telugu | Varanasi Movie Trailer | Mahesh Babu | SS Rajamouli
snippet.description:
Watch Varanasi Movie Story Explained in Telugu | Varanasi Movie Trailer | Mahesh Babu | SS Rajamouli


Varanasi promises a sweeping time-travel adventure rooted in Hindu mythology, with Rajamouli revealing that one major sequence is inspired by ‚Äúan important episode from the Ramayana.

Mahesh Babu, collaborating with Rajamouli for the first time. His introduction at the event ‚Äî riding a mechanical white bull ‚Äî mirrored his ferocious on-screen first look as a blood-streaked warrior wielding a trident.

Priyanka Chopra, returning to Indian cinema after several Hollywood projects, plays Mandakini. Prithviraj Sukumaran, introduced earlier this month as the antagonist Kumbha, described his role as ‚Äúphysically and emotionally exhausting,‚Äù

snippet.title: VARANASI to the WORLD Reaction! Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemondo!
snippet.description:
VARANASI to the WORLD Reaction! Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemondo! #varanasi #varanastrailer ##varanasitrailerreaction #ssrajamouli #trailerreaction Kathy and Mark react to Varanasi To the World! Varanasi (stylised as VƒÅranƒÅsi) is an upcoming Indian Telugu-language action-adventure film directed by S. S. Rajamouli, who co-wrote the screenplay with V. Vijayendra Prasad. T the film stars Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra and Prithviraj Sukumaran. Rajamouli conceived the film as a globetrotting action adventure rooted in Indian cultural themes, drawing inspiration from the structure and emotional tone of classic adventure cinema.

‡¶Ü‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡¶Æ‡¶æ ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡ß∞‡ßç‡¶ú‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶ï‡ß∞‡¶ø ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶¨ ‡¶¨‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡¶ø ‡¶Ü‡¶∂‡¶æ ‡ß∞‡¶æ‡¶ñ‡¶ø‡¶õ‡ßã‡¶Å ‡•§
       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.

snippet.description:
Presenting the official trailer of ek≈ç, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ek≈ç marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence ‚Äî exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

Stream and Listen to the teaser track 'Eko Intro Theme' on your favourite audio streaming platforms - http://tinysync.in/oG_f1C_xnAE

en.description:
Presenting the official trailer of ek≈ç, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ek≈ç marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence ‚Äî exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

snippet.title: TOWN HALL 18 IS HERE!
snippet.description:
A new Town Hall crash-lands, introducing a powerful new weapon: the Guardians! The Revenge Tower, Super Wizard Tower and the brand-new Totem Spell shake up the battlefield, while the Meteor Golem makes a triumphant return. Crafting Phase 2 brings three new Crafted Defenses! Finally, the Fancy Shop opens for business! Earn Sparky Stones for upgrading Crafted Defenses and Supercharging buildings to unlock unique rewards.



Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/
